embeds.title: Click For Notifications
embeds.description:
Want to be notified for a specific topic you're interested in? Click on the menu below this message.
​

fields.name: <:Server:1061829455506583602> Executives
fields.value: The people above everyone in the server (they can do something evil and no one can stop them). These people are usually owners and founders of a guild.

fields.name: <:Bullsht:1061829455506583602> Management
fields.value:
These are the people that do an Executive member's dirty work. They dictate the server (mainly people below them) and respect the Executive members.
**•**

fields.name: <:Events:1061829455506583602> Events
fields.value: Become  notified on game nights, special tryouts, giveaways, and more!

fields.name: <:Updates:1061829455506583602> Updates
fields.value: Become  notified when we annouce updated to the server.

fields.name: <:Lore:1061829455506583602> Lore Updates
fields.value: Become notified when there is a update on Site53's lore.
